# Titanic EDA & Feature Engineering

## Objective
Perform Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) and Feature Engineering on the Titanic dataset.

## Skills Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn

## Workflow
- Data Cleaning
- Missing Value Handling
- Outlier Detection
- Feature Engineering
- Visualization

## Result
Prepared a clean dataset ready for machine learning.
